      <title>特朗普在哈里斯正式获得提名前不会承诺参加辩论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/harris-says-she-ll-debate-trump-after-republican-balked-at-host</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在民主党候选人卡玛拉·哈里斯挑战共和党候选人出席先前安排的辩论后，唐纳德·特朗普的竞选团队拒绝承诺与这位候选人进行辩论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/harris-says-she-ll-debate-trump-after-republican-balked-at-host</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 19:46:29 GMT</pubDate>
